1. [ ] All icon methods defined with Unicode and ASCII variants
2. [ ] OutputContext correctly determines which to use
3. [ ] ASCII fallbacks are readable and meaningful
4. [ ] All icons return non-empty strings
5. [ ] Unit tests pass

