## Error Handling
All errors MUST be logged before propagating:
```rust
fn some_operation(&mut self) -> Result<T, E> {
    match inner_operation() {
        Ok(v) => Ok(v),
        Err(e) => {
            self.logger.error("Operation failed", &e);
            Err(e)
        }
    }
}
```

